### Hadith 2:616

*Narrated 'Ubaidullah bin 'Abdullah:*

Ibn Abbas' said, "Usama rode behind Allah's Apostle from 'Arafat to
Al-Muzdalifa; and then Al-Fadl rode behind Allah's Apostle from
Al-Muzdalifa to Mina." Ibn Abbas added, "Both of them said, 'The Prophet
kept on reciting Talbiya till he did the Rami of Jamrat-al-'Aqaba.' "

